Tɔmpiye paɣtʊ takayaɣ, palakɩ-ɖɩ nɛ tʊmɩyɛ ñamtʊ nɔmɔʊ taa kɛ kewiyaɣ ajaɛyaa sɔsɔnaa aŋgbaa ndɩ ndɩ taa. Mbʊ lɛ, pɔyɔɔdʊʊ OIT paɣtʊ takayaɣ tɔm, [[Eerɔpʋ tɛtʋ tɔm|Eerɔpʊ]] tambɔɔ paɣtʊ takayaɣ yaa ɛyaa sɔsaa paɣtʊ takayaɣ. Paa ɛzɩmta lɛ, kɛwɛ camɩyɛ cɩɖɩ cɩɖɩ yaa kpayɩ kpayɩ aŋgbaa a-naa a-taa se pɔyɔɔdɩ nɩnaʊ tɔm yaa kiɖe tɛ tɔm kɩlabɩtʊ.

